<span class="line">      <span class="token property">&quot;description&quot;</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">&quot;Apple MacBook Pro with M2 Pro chip, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD&quot;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span></span>
